This is Notodontidae Biodiversity data collected by Raymond Murphy for various places in Malawi. It has been mobilised as part of a BID project titled Strengthening Malawi's Biodiversity Information Facility. Some of the specimens have been donated to The Department of Museums and Monuments|183 occurrences
